    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Let An-gels’ ho-ly choirs be a-mazed at the won-der; and let us mor-tals cry out a hymn with our voic-es, be-hold-ing God’s mar--vel-lous con-de-scen-sion tran-scend--ing speech: He at Whom__ the pow-ers of the Heav-ens do trem-ble, Him do a--ged arms take in their ten-der em-brace now, the on-ly true Friend of man. \n\nthe on-ly true Friend__ of man.___"
    }
  }
